H. C. JONES, Collector of Internal Revenue for the District of Oklahoma, v. TOKLAN ROYALTY CORPORATION, a Corporation. No. 3127. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Feb. 27, 1945. Charles E. Dierker, U. S. Atty., of Oklahoma City, Old., for appellant. I. J. Underwood, of Tulsa, Okl., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Docketed and dismissed per stipulation.
